- pkgs/by-name/fo/foo/package.nix: line 10, column 14 has the following patch URL: "https://github.com/AndyLavr/amd-ucodegen/compare/0d34b54e396ef300d0364817e763d2c7d1ffff02...dobo90:amd-ucodegen:7a3c51e821df96910ecb05b22f3e4866b4fb85b2.patch".
